자백: 밤말은 쥐가 듣고 낮말은 새가 듣는다
jabaek: bammareun jwiga deutgo nanmareun saega deunneunda
jabaeg: bammal-eun jwiga deudgo najmal-eun saega deudneunda
chabaek: pammarŭn chwiga tŭtko nanmarŭn saega tŭnnŭnda
capayk: pammal.un cwika tutqko nacmal.un sayka tutnunta

jabaek: saehae bongmani badeuseyo/saehae bok mani badeuseyo
jabaeg: saehae bogmanh-i bad-euseyo/saehae bog manh-i bad-euseyo
chabaek: saehae pongmani padŭseyo/saehae pok mani padŭseyo
capayk: sayhay pokmanh.i pat.useyyo/sayhay pok manh.i pat.useyyo

자백: 콩 심은 데 콩 나고 팥 심은 데 팥 난다
jabaek: kong simeun de kong nago pat simeun de pat nanda
jabaeg: kong sim-eun de kong nago pat sim-eun de pat nanda
chabaek: k'ong simŭn te k'ong nago p'at simŭn te p'at nanda
capayk: khong sīm.un tey khong nako phath sīm.un tey phath nanta
